name: 4 Song Demo
description:
Four track debut demo from Before We Move On. Four death defying tracks self packaged in a shiny case with a nice cover and track listings.

	By purchasing this demo you not only get this but you get the satisfaction of knowing that you helped us out and that your money is going towards a full length c.d that we plan to release in the summer of 2007.

name: Spartan Helmet Tee
description: Join the BWMO army with our very first t-shirt. This t shirt is only available in black with the white Before We Move On Spartan Helmet for the time being. Available in Youth Large, Small, Medium and Large while quantities last!
